ğŸ“‚ 2. Development Guidelines
âŒ Do Not Use GOV.UK Macros
All components should be written using raw HTML rather than relying on GOV.UK Macros. This ensures that the application remains:
âœ… Easier to debug and customize
âœ… Independent of Nunjucks macros
âœ… More maintainable in the long run

